Attribution
-----------

This project is a hard fork of:

    eibrahim/freeresend
    https://github.com/eibrahim/freeresend
    Copyright (c) 2025 EliteCoders
    MIT License

Diverged at commit:

    3439985c3d9f5dc187acc75d8a063d31c3d5fe9f
    "add: umami + stripe metrics to stats reporter"
    2026-04-21T15:40:20-04:00

The diverge boundary is marked in this repository by the git tag
`v0.1.0-my-resend`. The full git history of the upstream project is
preserved (no squash) so that authorship of inherited code remains
visible via `git blame` and `git log`.

Optional upstream remote is configured fetch-only:

    git remote add upstream https://github.com/eibrahim/freeresend.git
    git remote set-url --push upstream no_push


Planned Divergence
------------------

The following changes distinguish my-resend from the upstream project
(some are still in progress; see the project plan for status):

  * AWS SDK migration: SES v1 (`@aws-sdk/client-ses`)
    -> SES v2 (`@aws-sdk/client-sesv2`)
  * DNS automation: DigitalOcean DNS only
    -> DigitalOcean DNS + AWS Route53, selectable at runtime via the
    `DNS_PROVIDER` environment variable
  * API key prefix: `frs_` -> `mrs_`
  * Branding, README localization (English + Korean), and full
    documentation rewrite
